Package: metaGLMM
Title: meta-analysis using generalized linear mixed effects model with aggregate data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Keisuke", "Hanada", , "keisuke.hanada@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The metaGLMM package extends traditional random-effects meta-analysis by embedding it within a generalized linear mixed-effects model framework, thereby enabling covariate adjustment and support for non-normal responses. This methodology was introduced in Hanada (2025).
